title: Immortal Emperor Xia Guixuan
description: Immortal Emperor Xia Guixuan ManhuaAn immortal emperor, Xia Guixuan, was defeated by his arch-enemy and went into seclusion in the core of a remote planet in the universe to heal his wounds. The planet’s environment was gradually transformed by his immortal spirit energy, turning it into a habitable planet with abundant spiritual energy. The original creatures began to transform into humans and develop their own civilisation. Some years later, human exploration ships from the galaxy arrived here. On all levels, unknown and powerful beings began to take aim at this place. Many sides collide and heroes rise. Ruling a Planet To Possess the Celestial Body To Possess the Heavenly Body Zuo Yong Xing Qiu 坐拥星球 Immortal Emperor Xia Guixuan Welcome to My Planet
